  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is to evaluate the highest tolerated dose, safety and activity of HCD122 in adults
      with non-Hodgkin's or Hodgkin's lymphoma who have received at least two prior therapies.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
